---
<section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-background border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight text-foreground font-bold mb-6">
          Ergebnisse statt KI-Hype
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Wir bei KI Automatisieren setzen auf messbare Resultate, nicht auf leere Versprechungen.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="relative group rounded-2xl bg-[#111827] border border-white/10 p-8 text-center hover:border-lime-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                <!-- Icon: Award -->
                <div class="w-12 h-12 text-lime-400">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="7"></circle><polyline points="8.21 13.89 7 23 12 20 17 23 15.79 13.88"></polyline></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground">
                    Qualität
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Unsere Lösungen basieren auf bewährten Best Practices und jahrelanger Erfahrung im deutschen Mittelstand.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="relative group rounded-2xl bg-[#111827] border border-white/10 p-8 text-center hover:border-lime-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                <!-- Icon: Cpu -->
                <div class="w-12 h-12 text-lime-400">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><rect x="9" y="9" width="6" height="6"></rect><line x1="9" y1="1" x2="9" y2="4"></line><line x1="15" y1="1" x2="15" y2="4"></line><line x1="9" y1="20" x2="9" y2="23"></line><line x1="15" y1="20" x2="15" y2="23"></line><line x1="20" y1="9" x2="23" y2="9"></line><line x1="20" y1="14" x2="23" y2="14"></line><line x1="1" y1="9" x2="4" y2="9"></line><line x1="1" y1="14" x2="4" y2="14"></line></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground">
                    Technologie
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Wir nutzen modernste KI-Modelle und Automatisierungs-Plattformen (N8N), um maximale Effizienz zu garantieren.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="relative group rounded-2xl bg-[#111827] border border-white/10 p-8 text-center hover:border-lime-500/50 transition-all duration-300">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-lime-500/5 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity rounded-2xl pointer-events-none"></div>
            <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
                <!-- Icon: Shield -->
                <div class="w-12 h-12 text-lime-400">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path></svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-foreground">
                    Datenhoheit
                </h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
                    Ihre Daten sind Ihr Kapital. Wir sorgen dafür, dass sie sicher verarbeitet werden (DSGVO-konform).
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
</section>
